---
title: Classic Roasted Pork Tenderloin and Sage Gravy with Corn, Zucchini and Sweet Potato Mash
description: Sage-scented pork tenderloin is a perfect idea for dinner! Served with tender sweet potatoes, zucchini and corn and smothered with a sage brown gravy. This one hits all the marks!

Ingredients: Pork tenderloin • Sweet potato • Zucchini • Thaw-friendly corn (corn, modified vinegar) • Garlic spread (margarine (soybean oil, water, modified palm and palm kernel oils, salt, vegetable monoglycerides, soy lecithin, potassium sorbate, natural flavour, citric acid, annatto and turmeric, vitamin A palmitate, vitamin D2), garlic, onion powder, water, salt, vegetable mono and diglycerides, maltodextrin, citric acid, parsley, natural flavour, xanthan gum, potassium sorbate, natural colour, vitamin E) (soy) • Gravy spice blend (wheat flour (wheat), dehydrated vegetables (garlic, onion), hydrolyzed proteins (soy), sugars (dextrose, maltodextrin), yeast extract, natural flavours, caramel colour, disodium inosinate, disodium guanylate) (soy, wheat) • Chicken broth concentrate (sugars (maltodextrin, sugar), chicken stock, chicken fat, chicken flavor (chicken broth, salt, flavoring, water, glutamic acid, chicken fat, chicken powder, xanthan gum, organic sunflower oil), salt, yeast extract, xanthan gum, natural flavor) • Sage.
